com.hazelcast.map.impl.eviction

Interface Evictor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EvictorImpl

    public interface Evictor
    Evicts a RecordStore.

    When the RecordStore needs to be evicted according to checkEvictable(com.hazelcast.map.impl.recordstore.RecordStore), Evictor removes records from RecordStore.
